{"tid":506610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[友情] 覺唔覺得有啲朋友乜都管住好煩","createTime":"2017-12-22T11:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T15:22:45.000Z","uid":153978,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9314190f388cbc8caa48a1a78aef227bd7bd29","tid":506610,"uid":153978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:13:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我係中學個陣識同個一班同學玩熟左 成日冇野做就一齊去下唱k打麻雀咁既 <br />\n咁依家大家都上晒大學 各散東西左 大家各自各都有新圈子 同中學同學明顯少見左好多<br />\n問題就出黎啦 嗰個管家婆性格既朋友就開始俾說話我地聽 話埋哂我地唔理佢 有新朋友得啦個啲說話 又ig 開po講到自己好慘俾人忽略又剩<br />\n大佬呀 你自己都有新圈子啦有冇人話你呀<br />\n點解我地同其他人出街又要同你匯報<br />\n點解我同其他朋友去旅行又要發我脾氣 仲要當街當行氹你先得 仲要西足全日面<br />\n依家同你拍拖咩 做個朋友去邊又要同你講 做咩又要講 冇講又要西面發脾氣 你又唔係我男/女朋友 真係好向左起向右走煩呀<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"1cb0aa703a98f944d67abfde8dca4a92046ff744","tid":506610,"uid":153978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:14:14.000Z","msg":"依家個個都疏遠你 開心未？"},{"pid":"981c700ceb4fa35290731db06934fb004e67f798","tid":506610,"uid":153978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:14:30.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0e75604c3ed8c6123e8b5efbfa096168d9902695","tid":506610,"uid":153978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:14:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"30088979e6a919b700716ccb20a1d95bfc92b3d3","tid":506610,"uid":153978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:14:50.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3be7a880772a777fc5c330152114d8fd0f26c6da","tid":506610,"uid":153978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5cb92aa96c08ea2ce7f802acf771bebd63e4604e","tid":506610,"uid":153978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"11b17e4ef57380cdaed569c86b95eb67920c068b","tid":506610,"uid":153978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"